{"tid":859680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公正選舉人人有責：請即舉報違規選舉廣告","createTime":"2018-10-12T16:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T10:25:48.000Z","uid":36901,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8e31e4fe5b618ad4a3c3bc75d6e04e8ffbff57b1","tid":859680,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T16:57:58.000Z","msg":"《選舉管理委員會（選舉程序）（立法會）規例》（第 541D 章）第 7 部的規定及選舉<br />\n管理委員會在立法會選舉活動指引的第八章『選舉廣告』所列的指引，必須予以遵從。<br />\n<br />\n相關資料<br />\n1.<a href=\"https://www.eac.gov.hk/pdf/legco/2018lcbe_kw/Conditions_for_Display_of_EAs_at_DS(Chi).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Flegco%2F2018lcbe_kw%2FConditions_for_Display_of_EAs_at_DS%28Chi%29.pdf&d=CqIc3p6sjccGyQYz4AQlkdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=90b8649a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.gov.hk/pdf/legco/2018lcbe_kw/Conditions_for_Display_of_EAs_at_DS(Chi).pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1481159/%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E3%80%8C%E6%97%97%E6%B5%B7%E3%80%8D%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%E3%80%80%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E6%8E%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1481159%2F%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2597%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%25B3%2595%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2580%2599%25E9%2581%25B8%25E4%25BA%25BA%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%25BE%2588%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%258E%259B&d=CqIc3p6sjccGyQYz4AQlkdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=c613b5c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1481159/%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E3%80%8C%E6%97%97%E6%B5%B7%E3%80%8D%E6%B6%89%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%E3%80%80%E5%80%99%E9%81%B8%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9A%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E6%8E%9B</a><br />\n<br />\n選舉管理委員會規定立法會選舉候選人，不得在欄杆展示直旗，以免干擾駕駛者和行人視線，但各政黨不同候選人都直旗飄揚，究竟當事人知不知道是違法呢？有候選人則解釋其他候選人都是這樣做，亦有候選人堅持繼續掛真旗宣傳，不認為影響駕駛者。<br />\n<br />\n候選人在擺放宣傳品前，<strong>須向選舉主任遞交承諾書，會遵守規定。《在指定展示位置展示選舉廣告所須遵守的條件》，規定不得在欄杆及圍欄或其附近展示易拉架及直旗。</strong><br />\n<br />\n擺放「禁區」包括：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>公家地的行人過路處的交通上游30米範圍內<br />\n巴士站、巴士總站或其附近地方的欄杆<br />\n行車道上的中央分隔欄<br />\n行人天橋的外部、快速公路和行車天橋<br />\n路牌、燈柱<br />\n投票站範圍內及外牆</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果發現有候選人違規亂掛宣傳廣告直旗，可以致電選舉管理委員會 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">選舉管理委員會投訴熱線: (852) 2827 7251 </span><br />\n通常辦公時間<br />\n星期一至五(公眾假期除外)：<br />\n上午9時至下午1時及下午2時至6時<br />\n<br />\n分區投訴電話<br />\n油 尖 旺 區\t2399 2753<br />\n深 水 埗 區\t2150 8138<br />\n九 龍 城 區\t3575 3958<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打發現違規街站、選舉宣傳，亦可試下影埋相，即接打去/email去１８２３，叫佢地轉介去選舉管理委員會/民政署投訴"},{"pid":"ebfcb24ff7c130a4ef7c2e8a2d2eef3eb4cc0968","tid":859680,"uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T17:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/010001_a2641c3d916fda24d95fd54fa22151be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F010001_a2641c3d916fda24d95fd54fa22151be.jpg&h=add0f692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到有違規街站宣傳直旗<br />\n1 .影相<br />\n2.電話舉報<br />\n3.用1823app再補文字投訴"},{"pid":"7dc6da3e248aaf841b738dd433d35643bb9064c7","tid":859680,"uid":3194,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T17:04:39.000Z","msg":"瘋狂投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做個盡責市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85dd6d6e8ddf3d4d05e2ff7c088bf5bd531774ae","tid":859680,"uid":36901,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T17:22:21.000Z","msg":"仲有維護廉潔選舉<br />\n屋企有長者快d forward 俾佢地<br />\n叫佢地幫忙提提d老友記<br />\n因收受禮物利益而投人票係犯法架<br />\n捉到隨時要坐監<br />\n唔好以身試法<br />\n發現有人提供利益賄選，唔好做共犯<br />\n立即打去icac舉報<br />\nicac舉報,密密實實,唔洗驚架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/011719_a1be58433603fb3276f17f2d6c2c9871.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F011719_a1be58433603fb3276f17f2d6c2c9871.jpg&h=31f3e9d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1bd6b291853665a678863f23fe10286dd50ef6b","tid":859680,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T17:31:12.000Z","msg":"正，狂撚咁投訴，做死班仆街"},{"pid":"bc4b5c7d9793f1cdef861e5e1e6dc34b41ea30d5","tid":859680,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T04:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b70d273b5de4eb60fd789e673d91949ab7c7a8","tid":859680,"uid":41693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T04:44:57.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n呢排見到條行人天橋插曬旗 <br />\n見到都煩 <br />\n建議大家一齊係到分享疑似違規廣告 影相+地點"},{"pid":"ae4c75f9197722e1bb1d0c246f78666f75e35248","tid":859680,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T04:47:54.000Z","msg":"做好市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4352e8f3e4ec689199737592bd0303113536b05","tid":859680,"uid":53683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T04:55:32.000Z","msg":"1823個app好方便<br />\n隨時見到隨時報<br />\n你投訴佢仲一定要開file<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedda21cb7367dd796a79443aceb9638dc5acbb9","tid":859680,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4352e8f3e4ec689199737592bd0303113536b05","tid":859680,"uid":53683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T04:55:32.000Z","msg":"1823個app好方便<br />\n隨時見到隨時報<br />\n你投訴佢仲一定要開file<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:46:36.000Z","msg":"冇錯，上次選舉實測試過係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9f8fd